text: Agnieszka Brandebura (born April 16, 1981, in Łódź) is a Polish rhythmic gymnast. Brandebura competed for Poland in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. There she was 13th in the qualification round and didn't advance to the final of 10 competitors. == References == == External links == * * * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Polish rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Sportspeople from Łódź
